                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9866" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2475</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">797 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">冰山慧谷：工业遗产“活化”为文旅新地标</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Dalian Bingshan Wisdom Park: &quot;Activation&quot; of industrial heritage as a new landmark of cultural tourism.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">姚宏，高栋，陈醉，钟子谦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连冰山慧谷发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">冰山慧谷；文旅活化；商业模式创新；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Dalian Bingshan Wisdom Park; Cultural and tourism activation; Business model innovation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本文介绍了大连冰山集团旗下的慧谷园区，从工业遗址到产业园区跨越与发展历程。园区在保留原有工业遗址的基础上进行改造和建设，成为大连地区集文化、科技、产业于一体的综合性园区。然而，运营过程中仍面临诸多难题，为解决这些问题，徐总带领团队通过租赁模式筑牢基础，完善配套企业服务，助力企业发展；提出“园中园”创新模式，实现资源共享，引入其他资本合作打开了冰山慧谷“资本参与”模式的文旅发展新阶段，通过卓有成效的运营逐步实现园区营收增长，同时升级为当地年轻人聚集的创业与潮玩社区。同时，工业遗产的活化也为冰山集团的主业不断赋能与引流，促进了整个集团的闭环价值增长。本案例侧重于对学生商业模式分析能力、战略决策能力的培养，掌握组织印记、商业模式、商业模式创新、商业模式创新动因等理论，并为其他工业企业整体搬迁后如何处置原工业用地，实现工业文化传承与经济效益双轮增长，提供了可供借鉴的经验。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This article introduces Dalian Bingshan Wisdom Park under Dalian Bingshan Group, covering its leap and development process from an industrial heritage site to an industrial park. The park has been renovated and constructed on the basis of preserving the original industrial heritage sites, and has become a comprehensive park integrating culture, technology and industry in the Dalian area. However, during the operation process, there are still many difficulties. To solve these problems, General Manager Xu led the team to consolidate the foundation through the leasing model, improve the supporting enterprise services, and assist the development of the enterprise. The innovative model of &quot;garden within a garden&quot; was proposed to achieve resource sharing and introduce other capital cooperation, opening up a new stage of cultural and tourism development of the &quot;capital participation&quot; model in Bingshan Wisdom Park. Through effective operation, the park&#39;s revenue has gradually increased, and at the same time, it has been upgraded to a community for local young people to start businesses and play trendy toys. Meanwhile, the revitalization of industrial heritage has continuously empowered and attracted traffic to the main business of Bingshan Group, promoting the closed-loop value growth of the entire group. This case focuses on cultivating students&#39; ability to analyze business models and make strategic decisions, enabling them to master theories such as organizational imprint, business models, business model innovation, and the driving forces behind business model innovation. It also provides referential experience for other industrial enterprises on how to dispose of the original industrial land after their overall relocation and achieve dual growth in industrial culture inheritance and economic benefits.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》、《商业模式》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织印记；魏朱六要素商业模式模型；商业模式创新；商业模式创新动因；资源拼凑理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
